{"tid":1398373,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"新人想上前線, 問有經驗人士有啲咩技巧或者避忌嘅事項","createTime":"2019-08-02T18:47:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:28:23.000Z","uid":82747,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"81a851ae10c41cb749fd54a900d52a70c66a1a1e","tid":1398373,"uid":82747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:47:19.000Z","msg":"以下係知道嘅野<br />\n<br />\n裝備: 頭盔, 眼罩, 豬嘴, 手套, 大袋, 遮, 雪糕筒, 水, 手造盾牌, 長褲, (冰袖?)<br />\n<br />\n要做嘅野: <br />\n1. 緊急時拉後前面個人嘅袋, 扯後佢個人<br />\n2. 唔好踢走啲催淚彈<br />\n3. 留意隔離左右嘅口頭訊息<br />\n4. 幫其他人擋一擋攻擊, e. g. 彈/棍<br />\n_______________________________<br />\n<br />\n以下係想知道嘅野<br />\n<br />\n- 如何有效令催淚彈遠離人群, 盡快消滅<br />\n- 如何有系統地齊上齊落, 分工合作<br />\n- 如何用現在資源抵擋對方嘅武器<br />\n- 如何喺混亂中令訊息嘅傳遞變流通, 真正be water, 話黎就黎話走就走<br />\n______________________________<br />\n<br />\n小妹虛心受教, 歡迎補充。"},{"pid":"14f02e3fb89bd5172689e55320ad172d4d216619","tid":1398373,"uid":70894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:51:28.000Z","msg":"心理準備 <br />\n冇心理準備 比枝槍你都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"681cc81e87de1e8bcf1fbf9ef0df6d2ba8a79ded","tid":1398373,"uid":82747,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"14f02e3fb89bd5172689e55320ad172d4d216619","tid":1398373,"uid":70894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:51:28.000Z","msg":"心理準備 <br />\n冇心理準備 比枝槍你都冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T18:56:07.000Z","msg":"問得就預咗, 比返少少實質嘅資訊, 唔該"},{"pid":"10f71bfb1dbba9465920e84b96b22356074afd7c","tid":1398373,"uid":162330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T19:03:41.000Z","msg":"勇敢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6084f305a796139e65166971f486952f053c91b3","tid":1398373,"uid":82747,"like":5,"di